{"tid":1486534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 不要忘記我地琴日點解行出嚟","createTime":"2019-08-19T01:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T02:11:55.000Z","uid":190579,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba569fb9dbc87ff23f897066779a3f19ee9553b","tid":1486534,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:57:06.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">琴日既目標係</span></ins><br />\n1) 表示民意完全冇割蓆6.16-8.18之間既所有衝擊行動，認同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和理勇武陰陽互補，缺一不可</strong></span>既抗爭模式<br />\n2) 同全世界講，香港人唔係恐怖份子<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而唔係</span></ins><br />\n1) 爭取牆內大6人認同<br />\n2) 出嚟遊行而唔食煙食彈<br />\n3) 睇madam對大波波<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>更加唔係</ins></span><br />\n1) 將抗爭變番14雨革既失敗模式<br />\n嘉年華式抗爭，比D掌聲自己，階段性勝利，政治潔癖，捉鬼割蔗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理勇武，陰陽互補。<br />\n<br />\n因時制宜，缺一不可。</span></div></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bf0db8d7c1908daac5c59e2875b322b1cd262622","tid":1486534,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56a8620c2077bb95bb3ca829550af4fe2ccfedf","tid":1486534,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5bab7d9a5fba3a5d1beb25281ab37dad349295","tid":1486534,"uid":97871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:58:23.000Z","msg":"團結d啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876b9efa57b815cf75dd7b28fb75742aeafe7167","tid":1486534,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"Set Deadline,  不分化，唔理勇唔勇武，和理非可以繼續做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://g2.dcdn.lt/images/pix/baltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fg2.dcdn.lt%2Fimages%2Fpix%2Fbaltijos-kelias-v-cepliausko-nuotr-65429744.jpg&h=6678ec11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">8月23日 人鏈：香港之路Hong Kong Way正！式！上！線！！！！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式名稱：香港之路 The Hong Kong Way<br />\n日期：２０１９年８月２３日（星期五）<br />\n集合地點：港島線及荃灣觀塘線沿線各港鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路線圖 (細節待定)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SOnPTuT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSOnPTuT.jpg&h=f65321a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大致分三段：<br />\n港島線（筲箕灣 &mdash; 堅尼地城）：13KM<br />\n荃灣線（黃埔 &mdash; 美孚）：7.02KM<br />\n觀塘線（深水埗 &mdash; 油塘）：12.6KM<br />\n<br />\n時序：<br />\n集合並在行人路上排隊 19:15-20:00<br />\n手牽手組人鏈 20:00-21:00<br />\n和平散去 21:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">快啲幫手開post宣傳<br />\n 整文宣！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065a75ed29d329ffe2f833665e0f491e4cab0c60","tid":1486534,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c3c0e58ddf7c539132cd3bf68f6b487cfe06cf","tid":14